data.description: Come check out this ranch on large lot in Auburn. Home sits on 1.39 acres in Auburn centrally located to downtown Auburn and a short drive to Bethlehem and 316. Inside the home has an open floor plan and a partially enclosed garage. Garage houses the laundry room and was closed off at one time. Kitchen has stained cabinets and laminate countertops. Living room has a large stone wood burning fireplace. The backyard is spacious and fenced. Storage shed also comes with the property.
